_sText:
Designed for GG ^^

I aimed to make a map that was playable with large teams, as well as 2v2 & 1v1, while keeping a quick pace to the rounds either way.

This is a quick compile of the map as it is currently; I believe there's a problem with the HDR cubemaps so they may not work properly, & also I'm thinking about lowering the parapets a touch in future versions, depends on if people like them as they are ^^

Total worktime; around 9 hours.

Comments appreciated!
